# Zentora – Package Booking Platform

A responsive travel package booking web app that allows users to explore and book customized travel packages with real-time filtering and dynamic pricing.

## 🌐 Live Demo
[Visit Zentora](https://zentoratravels.netlify.app/)


## 🚀 Features
- Responsive layout for all devices
- Real-time filtering by destination, price, and category
- Dynamic pricing based on selected options
- Validated booking forms with error handling    
- Clean and intuitive user interface
- Modular, scalable structure using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- HTML5
- CSS3 (Flexbox/Grid)
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

## 📦 Installation (for local use)
1. Clone the repository  
   `git clone https://github.com/darshanbhatarkar/zentora.git`
2. Open `index.html` in your browser

